subdefinitions.definition: A place in England : A village and civil parish in Torridge district, Devon ( OS grid ref SS4008 ) . A market town and civil parish in South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire ( OS grid ref ST6390 ) . A suburb of Bradford , West Yorkshire ( OS grid ref SE1933 ) .

A community and former town in the town of Blue Mountains , Grey County , Ontario , Canada .
A township in Chester County , Pennsylvania , United States .
